summary: This grouped bar chart has 6 categories of Power Type on the x axis representing 2 groups: 2011, and 2030.
Averaging these 2 groups, the highest category is found for Power Type Nuclear generation with a mean value of 216.5.
The lowest category is observed at Spent nuclear fuel reprocessing and secondary fuel that has a mean value of 6.0
showing a difference of 189.2% with the maximum value.
In case of Nuclear generation, 2011 shows more dominance than any other Power Type and it has the lowest value in Spent nuclear fuel reprocessing and secondary fuel.
